  <body>
  <div>
    <p>
A 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_dietitian">Dietitian</xref>
 is a 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_care_professional">CARE PROFESSIONAL</xref>
 who is registered with the 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_health_and_care_professions_council">Health and Care Professions Council</xref>.        </p>
    <p>
A 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_dietitian">Dietitian</xref>
 uses the science of nutrition to devise eating plans for 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENTS</xref>
 to treat medical conditions. They also work to promote good health by helping to facilitate a positive change in food choices amongst individuals, groups and communities.        </p>
